   215	
   216	Use `assets/shared/benchmark-report-template.md` for `benchmark-report.md` and `assets/shared/source-template.md` for `source.md`.
   217	
   218	Reference `references/shared/README.md` for deep overflow: it routes to the case studies, the report worked example, and common pitfalls.
