   379	## 8. SUCCESS CRITERIA
   380	
   381	- The consuming skill has a dated `mcp-server/benchmarks/benchmark-<YYYY-MM-DD>/` folder.
   382	- `benchmark-report.md` uses the ten-section structure and includes winner or status, aggregate table, methodology, candidate profiles, findings, caveats, recommendations, replay commands, and cross-links.
   383	- `source.md` points to the authoritative spec packet and maps reader questions to source files.
   384	- Raw artifacts are copied or intentionally omitted with a documented reason.
   385	- The benchmarks README index links the new folder and source packet.
   386	- Shared sk-doc validation passes for authored markdown, or any remaining issue is escalated with exact command output.
