.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-opencode/assets/scripts/README.md:27:Use this file to identify the folder boundary, the likely verification path, and the local source files that need sk-code conventions. Keep behavior details in source comments and higher-level workflow details in the owning `SKILL.md`.
