    38	
    39	## 2. QUICK START
    40	
    41	**Step 1: Confirm the owner.**
    42	
    43	Start with `.opencode/skills/sk-code/SKILL.md` for runtime routing and workflow boundaries.
    44	
    45	**Step 2: Inspect the local code.**
    46	
    47	```bash
    48	rg --files .opencode/skills/sk-code/code-opencode/assets/scripts
    49	```
