   442	
   443	## 6. SUCCESS CRITERIA
   444	
   445	- Review output is findings-first and severity-ordered.
   446	- `code-review` mode baseline + `sk-code` surface evidence contract is explicit in report context.
   447	- Security/correctness minimums are always covered.
   448	- Recommended fixes are actionable and scope-proportional.
