   463	
   464	### Manual Testing Playbook
   465	
   466	Manual testing scenarios for the `code-review` mode (of the sk-code family) live in `manual-testing-playbook/manual-testing-playbook.md` (root index) plus per-feature sub-files under `manual-testing-playbook/<topic>/<scenario>.md` (both the category folder and the scenario file use bare descriptive slugs, no numeric prefix). Run scenarios via `bash .opencode/skills/sk-doc/scripts/validate_document.py manual-testing-playbook/manual-testing-playbook.md` for structural validation; execute scenarios in opencode/Claude/OpenCode sessions for behavioral verification.
