.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/code-quality-checklist.md:15:# Code Quality Checklist
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/code-quality-checklist.md:16:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/code-quality-checklist.md:17:Correctness, performance, and boundary-condition checklist for identifying production-impacting quality defects.
