.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/code-quality-checklist.md:165:Surface portability: pair this baseline with surface-specific quality guidance from `sk-code`.
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:1:---
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:2:title: Fix Completeness Checklist
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:3:description: Checklist for turning review findings into complete fixes across same-class producers, consumers, algorithms, matrices, and hostile environments.
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:4:trigger_phrases:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:5:  - "fix completeness checklist"
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:6:  - "same class producer inventory"
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:7:  - "cross consumer fix proof"
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:8:  - "finding class classification"
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:9:  - "instance only opt out"
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:10:importance_tier: normal
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:11:contextType: implementation
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:12:version: 1.5.0.3
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:13:---
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:14:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:15:# Fix Completeness Checklist
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:16:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:17:Checklist for turning a review finding into a complete fix that covers same-class producers, consumers, changed algorithms, matrix coverage, and hostile runtime state.
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:18:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:19:## 1. OVERVIEW
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:20:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:21:### Purpose
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:22:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:23:Turn a review finding into a complete fix that covers same-class producers, consumers, changed algorithms, matrix coverage, and hostile runtime state, not just the one cited site.
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:24:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:25:### Usage
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:26:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:27:Use this when a finding becomes a fix: classify the finding, run the required inventories, and include the completion output before claiming done. A finding that meets the instance-only opt-out may use the narrow path with grep proof.
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:28:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:29:---
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:30:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:31:## 2. CLASSIFICATION
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:32:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:33:State one class for every actionable finding:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:34:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:35:| Class | Use When | Required Proof |
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:36:|-------|----------|----------------|
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:37:| `instance-only` | One cited site and grep proves no siblings or consumers | Exact grep command and result |
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:38:| `class-of-bug` | Same field/string/helper/error pattern can appear at sibling sites | Same-class producer inventory |
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:39:| `cross-consumer` | Changed policy/helper/field is observed by other handlers, status, DB, docs, or tests | Consumer inventory |
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:40:| `algorithmic` | Regex/parser/path/resolver/security logic is being changed | Invariant plus adversarial table tests |
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:41:| `matrix/evidence` | Env/default/per-call, full/incremental, fresh/stale, root shape, runtime, or doc evidence axes exist | Full row table and SHA/range pin |
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:42:| `test-isolation` | Env/global-state/singleton behavior is tested | Capture/restore proof and hostile env variant |
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:43:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:44:### Instance-Only Opt-Out
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:45:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:46:A finding may use the narrow fix path only when all are true:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:47:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:48:- It is not P0/P1 security, path, auth/authz, sandboxing, env precedence, schema, persistence, or public-response behavior.
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:49:- `rg` proves no same-class producer or consumer.
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:50:- Verification is local and cheap: one focused test, one doc row, or one static audit command.
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:51:- The fix response includes the exact command evidence for the opt-out.
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:52:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:53:Otherwise, run the full fix completeness checklist.
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:54:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:55:---
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:56:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:57:## 3. REQUIRED INVENTORIES
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:58:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:59:Same-class producers:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:60:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:61:```bash
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:62:rg -n '<field|string|helper|literal|error-pattern>' <changed-files-or-module>
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:63:rg -n 'errors\.push|warnings\.push|throw new Error|JSON.stringify|return \{.*error|message:' <changed-files-or-module>
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:64:```
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:65:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:66:Consumers:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:67:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:68:```bash
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:69:rg -n '<changedSymbol>|<changedConstant>|<changedPublicField>' . --glob '*.ts' --glob '*.js' --glob '*.md'
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:70:```
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:71:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:72:Algorithm smell:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:73:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:74:```bash
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:75:rg -n '\.replace\(|new RegExp|startsWith\(|includes\(|split\(' <changed-files>
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:76:```
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:77:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:78:Matrix/evidence:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:79:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:80:```bash
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:81:rg -n 'it\.each|test\.each|describe\.each|requirement-id|source:' <changed-tests-and-packet-docs>
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:82:git rev-parse --verify HEAD
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:83:git diff --name-only <FIX_SHA>^..<FIX_SHA>
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:84:```
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:85:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:86:Hostile env/global state:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:87:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:88:```bash
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:89:env <RELEVANT_ENV>=true <focused-test-command>
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:90:env -u <RELEVANT_ENV> <focused-test-command>
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:91:rg -n '<ENV_OR_GLOBAL_NAME>|original.*Env|afterEach|finally|reset\(' <changed-test-files>
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:92:```
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:93:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:94:---
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:95:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:96:## 4. COMPLETION OUTPUT
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:97:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:98:The fix response must include:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:99:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:100:- Changed files.
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:101:- Finding class table.
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:102:- Same-class producer inventory.
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:103:- Consumer inventory.
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:104:- Matrix rows added or verified.
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:105:- Hostile env command when relevant.
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:106:- Previously closed gates rechecked.
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:107:- Intentionally unchanged siblings/consumers with evidence.
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:108:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:109:---
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:110:
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:111:## 5. RELATED RESOURCES
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-review/assets/fix-completeness-checklist.md:112:
