.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/013-create-skill-alignment/plan.md:64:<!-- /ANCHOR:quality-gates -->
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/013-create-skill-alignment/plan.md:73:Template-plus-postcondition. Rendering establishes the hub's durable routing instruction; the selected onboarding mode establishes whether a valid manifest exists. The shared P3 predicate, not create-skill, decides whether the resulting hub is compiled-eligible.
