   110	
   111	| File Path | Change Type | Description |
   112	|-----------|-------------|-------------|
   113	| `012-default-on-decision/spec.md` | Create | This decision spec |
   114	| `012-default-on-decision/decision-record.md` | Create | The ruling, the verified evidence with file:line receipts, alternatives weighed, and the fallback/drift/observability contracts in full |
   115	| `012-default-on-decision/{plan.md, tasks.md, checklist.md, implementation-summary.md}` | Create | Level-3 planning, task breakdown, verification checklist, and Planned-state completion record |
   116	
   117	> This phase authors documentation and contracts only. No runtime file, `SKILL.md`, manifest, or scorer is edited here.
