   134	| REQ-005 | Record the P0→P4 migration map with reversibility and the frozen-scorer pin at every step, and name the runtime→spec-tree resolver coupling as a P0 remediation (promote the resolver to a stable runtime path OR document the coupling as an explicit drift source). | `decision-record.md` and `plan.md` carry the ordered P0→P4 map; each step names its rollback; the scorer pin and "no routing-decision change" invariant are restated per step. |
