.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/014-benchmark-alignment/plan.md:54:- [ ] Baseline hashes and legacy benchmark reports are captured.
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/014-benchmark-alignment/plan.md:78:- **Eligibility/status adapter**: decides whether compiled parity is required and why a sentinel occurred.
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/014-benchmark-alignment/plan.md:80:- **Normalizer**: maps legacy intents and compiled qualified targets through `mode-registry.json` into action/selection/ordered targets.
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/014-benchmark-alignment/plan.md:87:authored scenario + gold
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/014-benchmark-alignment/plan.md:113:| Shared status/eligibility API | Cause and expectation authority | Consume read-only | State-matrix tests |
