.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/034-skill-benchmark-codex-executor/review/iterations/iteration-005.md:48:| 1 | KEEP WITH QUALIFICATION | Exact qualification: apply only to gpt-5.6-luna xhigh/fast via cli-opencode on the fitted sk-code suite; require a gold-bearing holdout before generalizing. |
